<ShopGame>
To enable the system, Enable "1" to disable, Enable "0".

<LoadNpc>
LoadNpc, load new NPCs for the use of the GameShop system in different positions.
The maximum of npc that can be added is 10, Modify the index starting with 0, adding +1.
These NPCs must be added to the monstersetbase.

<System>;<Item_All>
System information, here you can modify the prices that will be added by options, 
as well as the maximum level that the items to buy will have and the maximum days that the items may have.

<System>;<Item_Fenrir>
For the original fenrir (13,37). You can modify the price that will be added according to the type of fenrir that they will buy.

<DarkWizard><DarkKnight><FairyElf><MagicGladiator><DarkLord><Summoner><RageFighter>
The system is differentiated by classes, you can add as many armor, wings, weapon, pets, jewelry, etc. According to the class.

-Add + Class:
Item_Type = item category. <0 - 15>
Item_Index = item index. <0 - 512>
Item_Price = Entrance price to buy the item.
Item_Time = If the item will have time, we put 1.
Coin_Type = Type of currency that will be used for your purchase. {0: Zen, 1: WcoinC, 2: WcoinP, 3: GlobinPoint}
-->

